title: Bobby Gives Update On First Date With Flight Attendant + Opinions On Kids Wearing Makeup
itunes:title: Bobby Gives Update On First Date With Flight Attendant + Opinions On Kids Wearing Makeup
description:
Bobby shares that he has a date set with the flight attendant he met recently. The show discusses their opinions on young children wearing makeup. Also, Jimmie Allen calls the show to talk about performing his cover of “Shallow.”
